title: 2020 CFB Pick Em Week 10
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco are back for another week of picks. This week we have the first ever guest in Pick Em history, coach Pat Hill joined the program to talk about his coaching career and get a peek at the trophy!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
